tember   is engaged in the production and marketing of titanium bearing mineral sands and titanium dioxide tio pigment the company also produces natural soda ash the company operates through two segments tio and alkali its tio segment includes exploration mining and beneficiation of mineral sands deposits production of titanium feedstock including chloride slag slag fines synthetic rutile and leucoxene pig iron and zircon production and marketing of tio and electrolytic manganese dioxide manufacturing and marketing which is primarily focused on battery materials and specialty boron products its alkali segment includes dry mining of trona ore underground at its westvaco facility secondary recovery of trona from previously dry mined areas underground at its westvaco and granger facilities through solution mining refining of raw trona ore into soda ash and specialty sodium alkali products and marketing sale and distribution of alkali productsthe companys tio is used in a range of products in the manufacturing of paint and other coatings plastics and paper and in a range of other applications including inks fibers rubber food cosmetics and pharmaceuticals the companys soda ash products are used by customers in the glass detergent and chemicals manufacturing industries the company has operations in north america europe south africa and the asiapacific region within its tio segment the company operates three pigment production facilities at locations such as hamilton mississippi botlek the netherlands and kwinana western australia it also operates three separate mining operations kwazulunatal kzn sands and namakwa sands both located in south africa and cooljarloo located in western australiathe companys kwazulunatal sands operations located in south africa consists of the fairbreeze mine a concentration plant a mineral separation plant and a smelter complex the companys namakwa sands operations located in south africa include the namakwa sands mine a primary concentration plant a secondary concentration plant a mineral separation plant and a smelter complex its western australia operations consists of the cooljarloo sands mine and concentration plant and the chandala processing plant which includes a mineral separation plant and a synthetic rutile plant as of december   the companys tio operations had a combined annual production capacity of approximately  metric tons mt of titanium feedstock which consisted of  mt of rutile and leucoxene  mt of synthetic rutile and  mt of titanium slag as of december   its tio operations produced approximately  mt of zircon and  mt of pig iron as of december   it supplied and marketed tio under the brand name tronox to approximately  customers in over  countriesthe company provides its soda ash to a range of industries such as flat glass container glass detergent and chemical manufacturing the company produces natural soda ash from a mineral called trona which it mines at two sites in the green river basin wyoming the companys wyoming facilities process the trona ore into chemically pure soda ash and specialty sodium products such as sodium bicarbonate baking soda the company sells soda ash directly to customers in the united states canada and europe and to the american natural soda ash corporation ansac it uses a portion of its soda ash at green river to produce specialty sodium products such as sodium bicarbonate and sodium sesquicarbonate that has uses in food animal feed pharmaceutical and medical applications as of december   its alkali segment produced approximately four million tons of soda ash and downstream specialty products trona is dry mined underground at its westvaco facility primarily through the operation of its longwall mining machine the company solution mines trona at both its westvaco and granger sites using secondary recovery techniques the sesqui and mono plants located at its westvaco site convert drymined trona into soda ash the company sells refined sodium sesquicarbonate under the names scarb and sesqui the company sells its alkaliproducts to customers directly in the united states canada the european community the european free trade area and the south african customs unionthe company competes with solvay chemicals ciner resources lp tata chemicals soda ash partners searles valley minerals church  dwight co natural soda llc chemours cristal global huntsman kronos worldwide inc lomon billions cnnc and blue star » full overview of troxn company address tronox ltd lot  mason road kwinana beach   was    p  company web links home page officers  directors name compensation ilan kaufthal  peter johnston  timothy carlson  jeanfrancois turgeon  richard muglia  » more officers  directors tronox ltd news brieftronox board elects ilan kaufthal nonexecutive chairman jun   brieftronox identified misstatement in selling generaladministrative expense for certain prior periods jun   brieftronox reports the passing of board chairman and former ceo may   brieftronox commences implementation of executive leadership transition plan may   brieftronox ceo thomas caseys  total compensation  mln vs  mln in  mar   » more troxn news related topics stocksstock screenerbasic materialsspecialty chemicals troxnew york stock quote  tronox ltd  bloomberg markets error could not add to watchlist x  watchlist tronox ltd troxus new york usd   as of  pm edt  open  day range    volume  previous close  wk range     yr return  before its here its on the bloomberg terminal learn more open  day range    volume  previous close  wk range     yr return  ytd return  current pe ratio ttm  earnings per share usd ttm  market cap b usd  shares outstanding m  pricesales ttm  dividend indicated gross yield  sector materials  price change  industry materials  price change  related videos there are currently no related videos for this ticker please check back later company news press releases  tronox stock soars with appointment of new cfo trox  investopedia there are currently no news