xide pigment tronox alkali electrolytic and specialty chemicals investor relations newsroom sustainability careers about tronox tronox limited is a global leader in the mining production and marketing of inorganic minerals and chemicals the company operates two vertically integrated businesses titanium dioxide tio and alkali chemicals the tio business mines and processes titanium ore zircon and other minerals and manufactures tio pigments that add brightness and durability to paints plastics paper and other everyday products the business operates mines and mineral processing plants in south africa and australia and pigment manufacturing plants in the united states the netherlands and australia tronox alkali is the world’s largest producer of natural soda ash offering a secure reliable and diverse range of highquality product choices the alkali business mines and processes trona ore and manufactures soda ash that is used in the production of glass detergent formulation chemical manufacturing pulp and paper production and water treatment it also produces sodium bicarbonate and other chemical compounds used in common industrial and household applications our main alkali operations are in green river wyoming usa home of the world’s largest trona ore deposit tronox also has an electrolytic and specialty chemicals business that provides innovative products to the energy storage paper automotive and pharmaceutical industries tronox’s diverse global workforce of  employees is committed to safe and sustainable business practices that bring value to its shareholders customers employees and the communities where we work and live the company operates more than  locations around the world with corporate offices in stamford connecticut usa kwinana western australia australia philadelphia pennsylvania usa and sandton gauteng south africa it has a research and development center in oklahoma city oklahoma usa tronox is listed on the new york stock exchange under the ticker symbol trox our values get a quick overview of the tronox strategy by clicking the image to enlarge it winning culture safety is our number one priority our values corporate citizenship strategy leadership board of directors leadership team global footprint interactive map botlek the netherlands hamilton mississippi us henderson nevada us kzn sands south africa namakwa sands south africa oklahoma city oklahoma usa perth australia tronox alkali wyoming usa office locations corporate offices tronox titanium dioxide pigment offices mineral sands tronox alkali sales and service tronox titanium dioxide pigment sales mineral sands sales tronox alkali sales supplier portal tronox procurement supplier standards data storage notice tronox alkali supplier information contact us   tronox limitedall rights reserved privacy policy  terms of use  site map tronox bag manufacturers  suppliers of tronox bag product and companyus import trade data — panjiva panjiva menu panjiva solutions buyers suppliers logistics governments analysts products platform enterprise api our data united states trade data mexico trade data brazil trade data central  south america data china trade data trendspotting panjiva research pricing search english español  demo request a demo  sign in suppliers  buyers products shipments loading search filters manufacturers of tronox bag and suppliers of tronox bag setalerts savesearch exportresults  results matching tronox bag sort by relevance number of matching shipments recency weighted matching shipments specialization  matching expertise length of time shipped total matching shipment volume kg supplier name az supplier name za number of total shipments highlow number of total shipments lowhigh tronox mineral sales pty ltd australia has verified thirdparty data  shipments match tronox bag  shipments total  mt coal based activated carbon rchd packed in  x kg bags on  palle ts for merchants reference only po …tronox mineral sales pty ltd tronox pigments holland bv nether