 soda ash is an essential component in making glass fiberglass detergents tableware lighting and display screens for consumer electronics  sodium bicarbonate commonly known as baking soda has countless applications including those in foods an array of consumer products and pharmaceuticals  scarb® is the preferred ingredient in animal feed to balance rumen ph and provide electrolytes for poultry and swine  sesqui™ sodium sesquicarbonate provides the silky clean feeling in bath salts and many cleaning compounds the green river operation has been mining trona for roughly seven decades and today produces more than  million short tons  million metric tons annually tronox alkali ships approximately  railcars and  truck orders of trona each year and we do it all more efficiently and economically on a delivered basis than synthetic competitors anywhere in the world tronox alkali has its corporate offices in philadelphia tronox tronox alkali tronox titanium dioxide regional web sites botlek netherlands perth australia contact us our company products tronox titanium dioxide mineral sands titanium dioxide pigment tronox alkali electrolytic and specialty chemicals investor relations newsroom sustainability careers a brighter future – from the ground up tronox limited recently announced a definitive agreement to acquire cristals tio assets read more view report tronox titanium dioxide and tronox electrolytic tronox alkali   tronox limitedall rights reserved privacy policy  terms of use  site map contact us  tronox tronox alkali tronox titanium dioxide regional web sites botlek netherlands perth australia contact us our company products tronox titanium dioxide mineral sands titanium dioxide pigment tronox alkali electrolytic and specialty chemicals investor relations newsroom sustainability careers contact us for inquiries regarding tronox titanium dioxide tronox alkali or electrolytic and specialty chemicals please use the following links tronox titanium dioxide tronox alkali el